<title>USA: Baldor Electric to buy back one mln shares.</title>
<headline>Baldor Electric to buy back one mln shares.</headline>
<dateline>FORT SMITH, Ark. 1996-11-05</dateline>
<text>
<p>Baldor Electric Co said on Tuesday that its board of directors authorized the repurchase of up to one million shares through December 31, 1997, or about three percent of its outstanding stock.</p>
<p>The company said shares would be used to meet stock option requirements, employee benefit plans and other needs.</p>
<p>Repurchases would be made both in the open market and through negotiated transactions, the company said.</p>
<p>They would depend on the company's needs, market conditions and other factors, it said.</p>
<p>-- New York newsdesk 212-859-1610</p>
</text>
